I am truly sorry for betraying the trust placed in me by my former boss and the café. I deeply regret the pain and inconvenience I have caused. I understand that I currently do not possess the financial means to repay the stolen amount, but I am determined to make amends. I plan to eventually repay my former boss for the losses incurred, once I am able to secure stable employment.

I am a 25-year-old individual who, prior to this incident, had no previous criminal record. I want to assure the court that this incident has been a wake-up call for me. I am committed to learning from my mistakes, seeking rehabilitation, and becoming a law-abiding citizen.

Considering my guilty plea, remorse, lack of prior offenses, and commitment to making amends, I kindly request the court's leniency in determining my punishment.

Respectfully,
Olivia Jones
